# Problem statement

@symptom direct Anthropic API access (x-api-key header, ANTHROPIC_API_KEY env, @anthropic-ai/sdk import, https://api.anthropic.com fetches) survives across the stack despite Sub-P fix landing the custom-provider-claude-cli loader patch (hive 52de1ee37). User-reported convergence trace: "ubu1 의 hive sub-agent 가 x-api-key 인증 헤더로 직접 Anthropic API 콜하는데 그 키가 invalid". Root cause: the SDK provider extension `custom-provider-anthropic` shipped alongside `custom-provider-claude-cli`; loader picks the SDK path on hosts where slot-pool path is unreachable.

@axis user requires (1) separate router module, (2) wire call sites to it, (3) chflags uchg lock the router. Mac OAuth slot pool is the SOLE credential path; remote dispatches needing LLM calls route back through Mac's hive CLI rather than calling Anthropic directly.

